    "multicolumn_PCwCdq": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_9TQCwM": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "left",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Greg_Portrait_1.png",
            "image_ratio": "portrait",
            "heading": "<em>\"The 13 ingredients of Coastline I consider to be foundational to the future of human health.\"</em>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>\"After reviewing thousands of research papers and analyzing countless supplement protocols, these 13 ingredients represent the gold standard. Each one has robust clinical evidence and addresses fundamental aspects of healthy aging that I see compromised in my practice every day.\"<br/><br/><strong>– Greg Potter, PhD, MSc</strong><br/><em>Sleep & Circadian Health Researcher</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_8wWFyg": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "left",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Nic_Portrait.png",
            "image_ratio": "portrait",
            "heading": "<em><strong>\"I value Coastline's quality, scientifically rigorous ingredients. It eliminates hassle with the greatest certainty of results.\"</strong></em>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>\"When I'm looking at a supplement, I'm considering two primary factors – one, is it noticeably effective as determined by, primarily, human trials, and two, is it dosed appropriately. Coastline does both to the fullest degree. Additionally, it does this in one simple supplement matrix that hits all aspects of healthspan, and with a certainty in quality.\"<br/><br/><strong>– Dr. Nicolas Verhoeven</strong><br/><em>Ph.D. in Molecular Medicine (Track: Physiology) M.S. Kinesiology - Exercise PhysiologyACSM CPT</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_DprhDY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "left",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CL-ChrisP-Scientist.png",
            "image_ratio": "portrait",
            "heading": "<em>\"Coastline represents a new era of precision supplementation — one rooted in clarity, science, and consistency.\"</em>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>\"Most supplements are built around marketing stories rather than measurable outcomes. What Coastline has done is strip away that noise and focus only on ingredients with real mechanistic data behind them — compounds that directly influence the pathways of cellular health, recovery, and longevity.</p><p>For me, that’s the future: fewer ingredients, more certainty, and an evidence-based foundation people can trust every single day.\"<br/><br/><strong>– Dr. Chris Pollock</strong></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_VfrfLJ": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "left",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Jessicabodasphotography-jacques.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "portrait",
            "heading": "<em><strong>\"Coastline is what happens when you combine scientific rigor with real-world clinical understanding.\"</strong></em>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>\"As a clinician, I’ve seen how confusing the supplement landscape can be — even for health professionals. Coastline takes a refreshingly disciplined approach: evidence-driven ingredients, clinically meaningful doses, and clear intent behind every inclusion.</p><p>It’s a formulation built not to follow trends, but to stand the test of time — one that truly supports the biology of aging from the inside out.\"</p><p>– <strong>Dr. Jacqueline Jacques, ND</strong><br/><em>Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine<br/>Clinical Nutrition Specialist</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_jLtiV3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "left",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Artboard_3_995cd844-996f-4435-a985-9d8fbd026b50.png",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<em><strong>\"Developed after a thorough evaluation of the latest advances in health sciences, Coastline represents the state of the art In longevity science.\"</strong></em>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>\"Coastline bridges cutting-edge aging research with practical human health. Its ingredients aren’t speculative — they’re backed by strong mechanistic evidence supporting cellular resilience and healthy aging. It’s a rare formulation that truly reflects where longevity science stands today.\"</p><p><strong>– João Pedro de Magalhães, PhD</strong><br/><em>Professor of Molecular Biogerontology<br/>Institute of Inflammation and Ageing, University of Birmingham</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
