    "portfolio_aVwBdh": {
      "type": "portfolio",
      "blocks": {
        "profile_tCLPJb": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_67.png",
            "heading": "Creatine Monohydrate - 5250 mg",
            "text": "<p>The gold standard form for cellular energy metabolism and cognitive function. Supports muscle strength, power output, and brain health while helping maintain ATP production - your body's primary energy currency. Research shows it may help preserve muscle mass and cognitive performance as you age, making everyday activities feel easier and supporting mental clarity throughout your day.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_chzmeA": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_54.png",
            "heading": "L-Glycine 5000 mg",
            "text": "<p>A foundational amino acid that's crucial for collagen synthesis, supporting healthy skin, joints, and connective tissues. Acts as a calming neurotransmitter that can improve sleep quality while supporting detoxification processes in the liver. As glycine production declines with age, supplementation helps maintain tissue repair, wound healing, and may support longevity pathways.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_BqCzEy": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_55.png",
            "heading": "Inulin (from Chicory) 4000 mg",
            "text": "<p>A premium prebiotic fiber that selectively feeds beneficial gut bacteria, supporting digestive health and immune function. Helps improve mineral absorption, particularly calcium and magnesium, while promoting regular bowel movements. A healthy gut microbiome is linked to better mood, immune response, and even cognitive function - making this a foundation for overall wellness.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_XX7ggm": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_60.png",
            "heading": "Taurine 3050 mg",
            "text": "<p>An essential amino acid that declines significantly with age, supporting cardiovascular health, exercise performance, and cellular protection. Helps regulate electrolyte balance, supports healthy blood pressure, and may improve insulin sensitivity. Research suggests taurine supplementation can help maintain youthful cellular function and energy levels as you age.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_fJ3gYf": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_57.png",
            "heading": "Glucosamine 750 mg",
            "text": "<p>A building block compound essential for healthy cartilage and joint function. Helps maintain joint mobility, reduces stiffness, and supports the body's natural ability to repair and maintain connective tissues. Particularly important as natural glucosamine production decreases with age, leading to joint discomfort and reduced mobility over time.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_dpiJz3": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/bizhillingdon_image_of_banana_slices_for_a_magnesium_ingredient_e1b70161-bc32-409d-ab0c-740ca755e575.png",
            "heading": "Magnesium Citrate 150 mg",
            "text": "<p>An essential mineral cofactor in over 300 enzymatic reactions, supporting energy production, muscle function, and nervous system health. Helps regulate blood sugar, supports bone health, and promotes restful sleep. Most people don't get enough magnesium from diet alone, making supplementation crucial for optimal cellular function and stress management.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_aHraB3": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_59.png",
            "heading": "L-Ergothioneine 5mg",
            "text": "<p>A powerful 'longevity vitamin' and master antioxidant that accumulates in tissues throughout the body, particularly the brain, heart, and liver. Provides cellular protection against oxidative stress and inflammation while supporting mitochondrial health. Research suggests it may help maintain cognitive function and support healthy aging at the cellular level.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "profile_tCLPJb",
