      "blocks": {
        "profile_6iypNX": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_56.png",
            "heading": "Coenzyme Q10 200 mg",
            "text": "<p>An essential cofactor for mitochondrial energy production, supporting heart health and cellular energy metabolism. Acts as a powerful antioxidant protecting cells from oxidative damage while supporting cardiovascular function. CoQ10 levels naturally decline with age, making supplementation important for maintaining energy levels, exercise performance, and long-term heart health.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_CJzzAD": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_63.png",
            "heading": "Lutein 10 mg",
            "text": "<p>A carotenoid antioxidant that selectively accumulates in the retina, providing protection against blue light damage and supporting long-term eye health. Helps maintain visual acuity, reduces eye strain from screen time, and may support cognitive function. As natural lutein leve</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
