          }
        },
        "profile_tEtbhX": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_62.png",
            "heading": "Zeaxanthin 2 mg",
            "text": "<p>Works synergistically with lutein to form the macular pigment, providing enhanced protection for the central retina and supporting sharp, clear vision. Helps filter harmful blue light, reduces glare sensitivity, and supports overall eye comfort during daily activities. Essential for maintaining long-term eye health and visual performance as you age.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_wjL8UK": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_63.png",
            "heading": "Astaxanthin 6 mg",
            "text": "<p>One of nature's most potent antioxidants, providing comprehensive cellular protection and supporting skin health, eye health, and exercise recovery. Helps reduce inflammation, supports cardiovascular health, and may improve skin elasticity and hydration. Research shows it can help reduce exercise-induced fatigue and support overall vitality and healthy aging.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        }
      },
