          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_65.png",
            "heading": "L-Theanine 200 mg",
            "text": "<p>An amino acid from tea that promotes calm, focused relaxation without drowsiness while supporting better sleep quality. Helps reduce stress and anxiety, promotes alpha brain wave activity associated with relaxed alertness, and can improve sleep onset and quality. Perfect for evening use to help you unwind and prepare for restorative sleep.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        }
