    "faq_64f36A": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_UMdW7G": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "When will I notice results?",
            "text": "<p>Most members report feeling more consistent energy within the first week, with sleep quality improvements often noticed within 3-5 days. More significant benefits like improved recovery and sustained vitality typically develop over 4-8 weeks of consistent use as your body reaches optimal nutrient levels.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_NMRfUD": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How is Coastline different from other supplements?",
            "text": "<p>Coastline is a complete AM/PM system targeting 11 body systems and 12 hallmarks of aging, not just isolated nutrients. We use research-backed dosages, third-party testing, and transparent labeling. No proprietary blends, artificial flavors, or under-dosed ingredients common in other products.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_7n7H8R": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I take Coastline with my current supplements?",
            "text": "<p>Coastline is designed as a comprehensive foundation, potentially replacing multiple individual supplements. However, we recommend consulting your healthcare provider before making changes to your current regimen, especially if you take medications or have health conditions.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_PgqVpU": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is your subscription policy?",
            "text": "<p>You're in complete control. Pause, skip, or cancel anytime through your account dashboard. No contracts, hidden fees, or cancellation hassles. We'll always show your next charge date and send reminders before processing orders.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_7ynfaq": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Coastline safe for long-term use?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, Coastline uses nutritional doses of ingredients that are generally recognized as safe for long-term use. All ingredients are third-party tested for purity and potency. However, we recommend periodic check-ins with your healthcare provider as part of your overall wellness routine.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_MhnXFE": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if I don't like it?",
            "text": "<p>We offer a 60-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied for any reason, contact our customer support team for a full refund. We want you to feel confident trying Coastline risk-free.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_76M9dY": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do you take Coastline?",
            "text": "<p>Take the Morning Blend and SoftGels with breakfast and the Evening Capsules ideally 1-hour before bed. This timing supports natural circadian rhythms and optimizes absorption. Each step is clearly labeled and contains the optimal daily dose.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_nDJmGf": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are there any side effects?",
            "text": "<p>Coastline uses ingredients at nutritional doses with excellent safety profiles. Some people may experience mild digestive changes initially as their body adjusts. If you experience any concerning symptoms, discontinue use and consult your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
